  "body": "## What's Changed\r\n* fix: skip cold start spans for provisioned concurrency by @litianningdatadog in https://github.com/DataDog/datadog-lambda-js/pull/734\r\n* chore: update tsconfig target by @rubenpad in https://github.com/DataDog/datadog-lambda-js/pull/712\r\n* Adding image integrity signatures for Gitlab images by @rithikanarayan in https://github.com/DataDog/datadog-lambda-js/pull/737\r\n* fix(http): `http.url` tag should contain the path by @CarlesDD in https://github.com/DataDog/datadog-lambda-js/pull/742\r\n* Add span.kind=server to aws.lambda spans by @jchrostek-dd in https://github.com/DataDog/datadog-lambda-js/pull/743\r\n* [Security] Pin GitHub Actions to a full-length commit SHA by @juliendoutre in https://github.com/DataDog/datadog-lambda-js/pull/745\r\n* chore(deps): bump `dd-trace` to v5.90.0 by @CarlesDD in https://github.com/DataDog/datadog-lambda-js/pull/746\r\n* v12.136.0 by @ojproductions in https://github.com/DataDog/datadog-lambda-js/pull/747\r\n\r\n>[!IMPORTANT]\r\n> This version imports `dd-trace-js` [v5.90.0](https://github.com/DataDog/dd-trace-js/releases/tag/v5.90.0)\r\n\r\n## New Contributors\r\n* @litianningdatadog made their first contribution in https://github.com/DataDog/datadog-lambda-js/pull/734\r\n* @rubenpad made their first contribution in https://github.com/DataDog/datadog-lambda-js/pull/712\r\n* @juliendoutre made their first contribution in https://github.com/DataDog/datadog-lambda-js/pull/745\r\n\r\n**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/DataDog/datadog-lambda-js/compare/v12.135.0...v12.136.0\r\n\r\n```yml\r\n# AWS Commercial\r\narn:aws:lambda:<AWS_REGION>:464622532012:layer:Datadog-Node18-x:136\r\narn:aws:lambda:<AWS_REGION>:464622532012:layer:Datadog-Node20-x:136\r\narn:aws:lambda:<AWS_REGION>:464622532012:layer:Datadog-Node22-x:136\r\narn:aws:lambda:<AWS_REGION>:464622532012:layer:Datadog-Node24-x:136\r\n\r\n# AWS GovCloud\r\narn:aws-us-gov:lambda:us-gov-<AWS_REGION>:002406178527:layer:Datadog-Node18-x:136\r\narn:aws-us-gov:lambda:us-gov-<AWS_REGION>:002406178527:layer:Datadog-Node20-x:136\r\narn:aws-us-gov:lambda:us-gov-<AWS_REGION>:002406178527:layer:Datadog-Node22-x:136\r\narn:aws-us-gov:lambda:us-gov-<AWS_REGION>:002406178527:layer:Datadog-Node24-x:136\r\n```",
